Package io.cyborgcode.roa.ui.service.fluent

Class RadioServiceFluent<T extends UiServiceFluent<?>>

java.lang.Object
io.cyborgcode.roa.ui.service.fluent.RadioServiceFluent<T>
All Implemented Interfaces:
io.cyborgcode.roa.ui.insertion.Insertion
public class RadioServiceFluent<T extends UiServiceFluent<?>> extends Object implements io.cyborgcode.roa.ui.insertion.Insertion
A fluent service class for interacting with radio button components in a UI automation framework.

Provides methods for selecting, validating, enabling, and retrieving radio button values.

The generic type T represents the UI service fluent implementation that extends UiServiceFluent, enabling method chaining for seamless interaction.
